1
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:58,720
Madam is here.

2
00:00:58,920 --> 00:00:59,480
Madam,

3
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,400
my vegetables,

4
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:02,060
don't have a single wormhole.

5
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,080
No wormholes.

6
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:05,560
Exactly, Yanmeir.

7
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:06,360
Look,

8
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,360
I picked the best vegetables.

9
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:11,640
We wanted thirty catties for one hundred and fifty wen.

10
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,640
You peeled off the rotten parts

11
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,500
and the worm-eaten outer leaves.

12
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:16,160
They look fresh now,

13
00:01:16,360 --> 00:01:18,120
but is there still thirty catties?

14
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:18,840
Yes.

15
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:19,760
Yes.

16
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,080
There definitely is.

17
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,760
Stinky Fish Zhang, did you bring your scale?

18
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,490
Why don't you

19
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:26,120
weigh it for me?

20
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,520
My scale

21
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,320
is too dirty.

22
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,479
Forget it.

23
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:34,620
We're old acquaintances.

24
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:36,200
I won't make things difficult for you.

25
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,130
One hundred wen.

26
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,120
I'll take all these vegetables.

27
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:41,450
One hundred wen won't even cover the cost.

28
00:01:41,479 --> 00:01:43,410
You're doing this on purpose. I...

29
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,460
Is that how you speak to Madam?

30
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:46,720
Okay.

31
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,120
All right. Thank you, Madam.

32
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:52,400
I don't want the ones on the ground.

33
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,400
It's filthy.

34
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,890
It's not fit for humans.

35
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:55,970
Mrs. Liu.

36
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:59,640
Take it back and stew it with tofu yourself.

37
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:05,360
Madam.

38
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:08,720
I guarantee the weight of my fish.

39
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,050
It's very fresh.

40
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,080
From today on,

41
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:15,020
I'm going vegetarian.

42
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:16,650
Fish, shrimp, and such,

43
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,280
don't bring them anymore.

44
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,340
I deliver my fish exclusively to you.

45
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,800
And now you just refuse them?

46
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,120
Are you playing me?

47
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,720
Stinking fishmonger.

48
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:28,720
Watch your mouth.

49
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,160
You have a death wish?

50
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,600
Think before you speak next time.

51
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:36,800
Laipitou.

52
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:39,320
Your furs are quite nice.

53
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,680
You have a good eye, Madam.

54
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,320
These furs

55
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,780
are all tanned using top-quality hides.

56
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:44,560
Yes.

57
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,600
Buy them all.

58
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,400
At market price.

59
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,600
Don't short them a single penny.

60
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,960
Come on.

61
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,360
Women like this

62
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,900
are the most interesting.

63
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,440
Qiu Ya,

64
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,320
you've become

65
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,160
a big reporter too.

66
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,360
Hello, Uncle Song.

67
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,400
I just started my internship.

68
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,800
How is your father?

69
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:13,720
I haven't seen President Qiu in a long time.

70
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,560
My father went to Europe on business recently.

71
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,720
He talks about you often.

72
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:18,520
By the way, let me introduce someone.

73
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:21,650
This is the eldest son of the Renjin Chamber of Commerce.

74
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:22,560
Hello, Director Song.

75
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,420
I am Ji Wenxuan.

76
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,440
A young talent.

77
00:03:27,079 --> 00:03:27,840
Not bad.

78
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,760
What brings you here?

79
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,600
Didn't the White Hair Blood Corpse Case

80
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,920
happen in Shencheng recently?

81
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,360
I want to conduct an exclusive interview

82
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:37,020
for the Shenmin Evening News.

83
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,440
I see.

84
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,400
Actually,

85
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,560
there's nothing strange about this case.

86
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,400
It was just a drug addict with albinism

87
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,660
who died on a rickshaw.

88
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:46,079
But I heard

89
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,640
that the deceased was murdered.

90
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,440
The killer must be someone else.

91
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,780
I'm sorry, Uncle Song.

92
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,280
I shouldn't have acted on my own.

93
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,400
It doesn't matter.

94
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,840
That rickshaw puller is ignorant.

95
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,600
He was taught a lesson and released.

96
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,840
The case is closed.

97
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:02,360
So it was just a false rumor.

98
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,020
Uncle Song,

99
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,260
have there been any

100
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,460
strange cases around here recently?

101
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:07,960
The case is closed.

102
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,560
Qiu Ya,

103
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:09,760
come to my office.

104
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,480
I'll fill you in on the details.

105
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,610
Mr. Ji, come with us.

106
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,440
No need.

107
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,320
You two go ahead.

108
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,380
I'll wait outside.

109
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:16,279
Alright.

110
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:16,890
Let's go.

111
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:17,420
Come on.

112
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,680
Officer Yao,

113
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:34,850
I'm leaving.

114
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:37,970
Officer Yao,

115
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:40,480
why do you look so unhappy?

116
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:43,200
The case was ruled as a misunderstanding involving sudden death.

117
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,400
Everyone was released.

118
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,530
You should be happy.

119
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:51,240
I think our investigation is on the right track.

120
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,780
I think someone committed murder

121
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,730
and moved the body using the smoke.

122
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:59,040
Even if your chief wants to close the case hastily,

123
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,970
I hope you'll keep investigating.

124
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,480
How?

125
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,720
The chief said

126
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:05,970
no supernatural nonsense is allowed.

127
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:08,160
And this Zheng Jinxian is nowhere to be found.

128
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,200
By the time he comes back,

129
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,800
the case will be long closed.

130
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:11,760
So,

131
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,760
we have to find evidence of the body being moved first.

132
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,490
Listen to me.

133
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,640
I found a box.

134
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,600
Enough.

135
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,600
Your business here is done.

136
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,320
Go back now.

137
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,560
As for earlier,

138
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:27,040
thanks.

139
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,160
I will help you find the evidence.

140
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,360
Don't give up easily.

141
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,700
Going home?

142
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,490
I can give you a ride.

143
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,200
Young Master Ji,

144
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:49,320
moonlighting as a driver for extra cash?

145
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:51,450
You're so keen on driving people home.

146
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,880
Why don't you drive that reporter lady?

147
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:56,400
She went to report on some teacher.

148
00:05:57,159 --> 00:05:59,020
By the way, I've driven you twice.

149
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,640
You haven't said thank you once.

150
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,640
Instead, you keep taking jabs at me.

151
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:04,930
I'm afraid I can't pay you back.

152
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,380
I don't need money.

153
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,720
It's just that...

154
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:09,920
your eyes

155
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,340
remind me of an old friend.

156
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:13,800
So,

157
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,900
I want to do a good deed.

158
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,160
Ex-girlfriend?

159
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,440
Cliché.

160
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,490
I really don't need to pay you back?

161
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:29,680
No.

162
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,370
Then take me somewhere.

163
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:38,880
Thank you, Madam.

164
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,260
From now on, if vegetable or fish sellers

165
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,970
dare to step near the Zheng Residence,

166
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:46,600
beat them on sight.

167
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,040
Here is a reward.

168
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,770
Understood.

169
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,880
Just watch, Madam.

170
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:52,440
I promise to use all my strength.

171
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:55,880
Even dressed well, she's still a lowly wretch.

172
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,400
What a sin.

173
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,680
It's a pity about my vegetable leaves.

174
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,080
Ma'am.

175
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,400
Ma'am,

176
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,320
I'd like to ask you something.

177
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:05,250
Do you know about the Zheng family?

178
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,780
I don't know. I don't know.

179
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:07,420
Auntie,

180
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,660
how about this.

181
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:09,880
For one question,

182
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,370
we'll give you ten yuan.

183
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,480
Ask away. Ask away.

184
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:18,160
I've lived on this street for most of my life.

185
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,960
There isn't any family gossip I don't know about.

186
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:25,480
That Mrs. Zheng,

187
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,660
do you know her?

188
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,360
That slut?

189
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,520
Of course I know her.

190
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:35,050
She is just a young widow who lost her husband.

191
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:38,280
Sister, try to move on.

192
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,560
My husband has been gone for over ten years,

193
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,560
but I still live a good life, don't I?

194
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,720
He must have been in so much pain.

195
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:49,850
A perfectly healthy person, his body burned to ruin.

196
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,720
He died from the sheer pain.

197
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:57,040
Here.

198
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,920
Take this home to eat.

199
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:01,920
You can't be hard on your own body.

200
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,600
Death brings relief to the departed,

201
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,000
but for us living folks,

202
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,460
we have to keep suffering.

203
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,180
Thank you, Sixth Aunt.

204
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,640
Don't mention it.

205
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:13,400
We are all neighbors here.

206
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:15,380
We have to look out for each other.

207
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,280
Sister,

208
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:21,200
your skills are getting better and better.

209
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,760
I'll show it around to more people.

210
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,560
Your business

211
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,000
will surely flourish.

212
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,419
She came to the Zheng family as a maid.

213
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,880
But who would have guessed? In the blink of an eye,

214
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,210
she became a concubine.

215
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:39,400
If you want to live well in this world,

216
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:41,530
you have to be shameless and ruthless.

217
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:44,560
What about Master Zheng?

218
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,980
Have you seen him go out recently?

219
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,840
Master Zheng?

220
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,400
He smokes opium all day long.

221
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,560
He never goes out.

222
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,760
Ever since he got vitiligo two years ago,

223
00:08:57,920 --> 00:09:00,720
Gu Mancang has been handling the business for him.

224
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,000
Gu Mancang?

225
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,440
Is this him?

226
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,960
That's not Gu Mancang.

227
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,360
That's Master Zheng.

228
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:13,180
Why is there no beard in this picture?

229
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,690
You said this isn't Gu Mancang.

230
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,720
How old is he then?

231
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,880
He's just over forty.

232
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:29,360
He's always carrying on with the Madam.

233
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:31,360
I reckon Ma Yanmei

234
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,720
is just waiting for the Master to die.

235
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:36,900
Then she'll take the money and run off with the steward.

236
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:37,720
All right.

237
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,480
That's all I need to know.

238
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,240
Thank you.

239
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:45,000
You two make such a lovely couple.

240
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,160
Let's go.

241
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,920
Ma'am, these were just caught this morning.

242
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,050
They are very fresh.

243
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,260
Take your pick.

244
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:05,040
The fish are mostly dead by now.

245
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,440
I'll sell them to you cheap.

246
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,600
I want this live one.

247
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,560
Ah Feng loves this fish the most.

248
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:11,160
It's an offering for Ah Feng?

249
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,560
You treat the dead so well.

250
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,490
Whoever marries you is a lucky man.

251
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:18,160
This is over a kilo.

252
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,500
That'll be 30 yuan.

253
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,800
30?

254
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,130
Is that all you have?

255
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,850
It's just for show for the dead.

256
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:29,530
This one.

257
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,780
I'll sell it to you for 10 yuan.

258
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,040
It's just dead, that's all.

259
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,640
No. Ah Feng loves live ones.

260
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,260
Brother Zhang.

261
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,050
For the rest,

262
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:40,000
can I use these shoes to cover it?

263
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:47,120
I'm out on the water all day.

264
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,720
I can't wear such nice cloth shoes.

265
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,180
No, Brother Zhang.

266
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,960
I stitched these thick soles myself, stitch by stitch.

267
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:56,040
I didn't cut any corners. They last a long time.

268
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,700
I usually sell them for forty.

269
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,080
How about you be with me?

270
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,520
I promise you'll have fish to eat every day.

271
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:02,560
Okay, girl?

272
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:03,900
Brother Zhang,

273
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,060
don't be like this.

274
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,360
Sleep with me.

275
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,090
It won't cost you a cent.

276
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,840
And there'll be more later.

277
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,300
Brother Zhang.

278
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,880
Take these shoes and call it even.

279
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:15,480
As for what you said,

280
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,140
I'll pretend I never heard it.

281
00:11:24,400 --> 00:11:24,920
Madam.

282
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,120
Do you want me to pack dinner for him?

283
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:28,440
Go ahead.

284
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:30,640
After all,

285
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:34,000
this is his last meal.

286
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:35,480
Yes, Madam.

287
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:37,280
And,

288
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,580
send a message to Lai Pitou for me.

289
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,720
It's so hot.

290
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,080
That explains it.

291
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:59,080
It's just like what we thought.

292
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,170
It's simple.

293
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:01,800
Disguise,

294
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,720
call a rickshaw,

295
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,680
and dump the body.

296
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:04,280
Frame him.

297
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:06,600
You mean

298
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:09,210
the real Gu Mancang killed Zheng Jinxian,

299
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,250
disguised the body as himself,

300
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,000
then pretended to be him

301
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:15,200
to take over Zheng Jinxian's identity?

302
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:16,960
In that case,

303
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:20,200
no one would notice Master Zheng died.

304
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:22,080
The dead one

305
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:24,340
is just a resigned butler.

306
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,610
How do you know everything?

307
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,040
During the day,

308
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:32,170
Qiu Ya was in the car,

309
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:34,080
asking Officer Yao about the case.

310
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,340
It was hard not to hear.

311
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,040
But

312
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,920
they are two different people.

313
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:46,260
Can changing a beard style

314
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,440
really fool everyone?

315
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:53,280
So this Ma Yanmei

316
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:55,130
must have been part of the plan.

317
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,720
That's why the Zheng family

318
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:58,250
replaced all the servants.

319
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,360
Right.

320
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:01,640
We must tell Yao Zhidi

321
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:03,520
about these clues immediately.

322
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:08,720
Sun Sheng,

323
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,250
come out with me.

324
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,000
What for?

325
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:11,760
Patrol.

326
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,440
So this is where you live.

327
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:31,600
Last time you only let me drop you off at the intersection.

328
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,560
One can't be too careful.

329
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:38,640
I won't invite you in.

330
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:44,480
So you work as a medium?

331
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,840
Just making a living.

332
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:47,170
Okay.

333
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:48,840
I hope I get the chance

334
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,160
to see your skills.

335
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,480
Sure.

336
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,400
If you want a reading,

337
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:55,080
I'll give you a discount

338
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,520
to cover the fare.

339
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:57,620
It's a deal.

340
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,080
See you.

341
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:06,040
Hasn't the case been closed?

342
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:07,920
Why are we still out on extra patrol?

343
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:08,720
It's the middle of the night.

344
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:10,280
It hasn't been safe here lately.

345
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:11,880
The captain told us to keep a close watch

346
00:14:11,880 --> 00:14:13,600
and look out for suspicious people.

347
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:14,680
A mission in the middle of the night.

348
00:14:14,680 --> 00:14:16,360
And you broke down.

349
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:19,490
This piece of junk. I'll replace you sooner or later.

350
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,130
Let's go.

351
00:14:21,520 --> 00:14:22,520
Let's take a look.

352
00:14:35,160 --> 00:14:35,890
Who's there?

353
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:40,680
Don't move.

354
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:41,440
Don't hit me.

355
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:42,320
It hurts.

356
00:14:42,400 --> 00:14:43,720
I didn't do anything.

357
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:44,760
There's someone else.

358
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:45,360
It's the middle of the night.

359
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:46,820
Why are you kneeling here?

360
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,320
I'm talking to you.

361
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,200
Get up.

362
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:54,600
Yao Zhidi.

363
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:55,640
Yao Zhidi, come take a look.

364
00:14:55,640 --> 00:14:56,760
What's wrong? There's a dead body here.

365
00:14:56,760 --> 00:14:57,600
It hurts! It hurts!

366
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,040
Behave yourself.

367
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:59,570
Why are you handcuffing me?

368
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:07,200
I'll secure the scene here.

369
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,060
You go get help.

370
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,680
I brought two guys with me.

371
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:24,540
Forensic Doctor Yang is here too.

372
00:15:24,640 --> 00:15:25,040
Talk.

373
00:15:25,520 --> 00:15:26,650
Why did you kill him?

374
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:27,960
Officer,

375
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,800
I really didn't kill him.

376
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:31,800
I was just out for a stroll tonight.

377
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:32,800
I passed by the General Temple.

378
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:34,320
I wanted to pay my respects to the General.

379
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:36,520
But as soon as I came in, I saw a dead body.

380
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:37,840
It scared me to death.

381
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:39,760
I was just about to run when you showed up.

382
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:40,820
Not a word of truth.

383
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,240
Looks like we need to loosen your skin a bit.

384
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,000
We have to.

385
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:44,520
No, no, no.

386
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:45,920
Tell the truth! Tell the truth!

387
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,680
- Will you tell the truth?
- I didn't kill him!

388
00:15:47,680 --> 00:15:48,680
Still won't talk?

389
00:15:49,280 --> 00:15:50,840
I really didn't kill him!

390
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,360
Why do I have to work overtime again?

391
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:55,960
Are there no human rights left?

392
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:57,560
Take a look. How did he die?
